{"tid":915293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東奧正名公投未過關 國台辦：代表不得人心 搞台獨註定失敗","createTime":"2018-11-25T01:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T09:56:21.000Z","uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0d1c8fc7336bac7344da41745127275f963f6a","tid":915293,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"九合一大選綁公投，東奧正名公投也正式登場，昨日確定公投未過關。對此大陸國台辦發言人馬曉光25日表示，所謂「奧運正名公投」案遭到挫敗，說明拿臺灣運動員的利益做賭注不得人心，搞「台獨」註定失敗。<br />\n<br />\n命題為：「第13案：你是否同意，以「台灣」（Taiwan）為全名申請參加所有國際運動賽事及2020年東京奧運？」結果最終開票結果以「不同意」較多，以5,771,111擊敗，蓋下「同意」的民眾4,760,833票。"},{"pid":"722f2b2b66cf9f2da6eefbfb276ec9f62f95644d","tid":915293,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b5015dbfc6d12bd422bb4e6ee0a5e9e5057b11","tid":915293,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"如果而家搞台獨公投都未必過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338c2b5a25b51e3f39371c0fed1a1a2f8816fc0c","tid":915293,"uid":57376,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:10:42.000Z","msg":"台狗以後連吠都無資格吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條路自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0bcabb7d0ead97ab66d6797683991fc0f38190","tid":915293,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:15:31.000Z","msg":"但我都係講緊台灣國"},{"pid":"c77b9c6d1c81be19f0229b5a9cb0a0bc560ab38a","tid":915293,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d3b17865f6768a86ed83c02d0ae176f81e1e11","tid":915293,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"永遠維持現狀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f98b0a2a729e5e783cb6fdb53b933bd767155f","tid":915293,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"16年果陣又唔見佢出黎吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a402b349a0870fbd489cc86863d26d1a23dba1","tid":915293,"uid":71583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"台灣有公投，香港、中國有冇？<br />\n一個太監笑人有J但冇結婚，不過個太監連打J嘅享樂都冇，失禁、成身尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國搞衰完一個香港仲未夠，仲要搞衰埋台灣<br />\n究竟中國人知唔知自己污染緊全世界"},{"pid":"b1483dbaa495e081153d1d04c71c6d6f0ec5f905","tid":915293,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"台獨跟參加奧會正名<br />\n根本係兩樣嘢"},{"pid":"4be5b1a051ffea346bd14abdc9d0a121796fcb64","tid":915293,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52f98b0a2a729e5e783cb6fdb53b933bd767155f","tid":915293,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"16年果陣又唔見佢出黎吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"支共特色<br />\n對自己有利<br />\n當然要打鑼打鼓宣傳"},{"pid":"9bab2143d9ec8ee0e067ac529bcfd6a3a306ae74","tid":915293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/1z4Sw4Kh/2018-TW-Election.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F1z4Sw4Kh%2F2018-TW-Election.jpg&h=c8edc3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef1324ceb5c70948ba0a71bb1d8bf005628b1e","tid":915293,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bab2143d9ec8ee0e067ac529bcfd6a3a306ae74","tid":915293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img 